Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,, fascinate: v.   迷住，吸引住\N One of the things that fascinates us most about cats is the popular belief that they have nine lives.\N我们对猫最吸引我们的一件事是普遍认为他们有九种生命。
